Sketch Bin - A simple Drawing Pad!
This is a simplified version of Spark Sketch.

Spark Sketch is an online paint app with social network sharing enabled. You can
paint what you want and share it with your friends. Then they can adjust it
and send it back to you.

Requires:
* PHP 5.3.x
* MySQL 5.x
* At least 100 MB space

This version is based on Spark Sketch 0.3.3.
